# SYNOPSIS
#
#   AX_HAVE_RAINBACK
#
# DESCRIPTION
#
#   Test for @PACKAGE_NAME@
#
#   This macro calls:
#
#     AC_SUBST(RAINBACK_INCLUDE)
#     AC_SUBST(RAINBACK_LIBS)
#
#   And sets:
#
#     HAVE_RAINBACK
#
